《变形金刚》的粉丝对电影中许多角色风格激进的重新设定评价不一，不过选择彼得·庫倫来为擎天柱配音之举获得了热烈好评<ref name="theirwar" />。《变形金刚》的漫画作者西蒙·福尔曼和《[[百變金剛_(影集)|百變金剛]]》的脚本顾问本森·议（{{lang|en|Benson Yee}}）都称赞这是一部壮观而充满乐趣的电影，不过福尔曼觉得片中人类的故事情节有些太多了<ref>{{cite news |title=Transformers Writer Simon Furman Interview |work=ENI |date=2007-07-31 |url=http://enewsi.com/news.php?catid=261&itemid=11481 |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2012-05-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120513024717/http://enewsi.com/news.php?catid=261&itemid=11481 }}</ref>。而议则感觉作为一个系列的开山之作，电影需要建好大部分虚拟宇宙，因此没有足够的时间细述霸天虎的故事<ref>{{cite news |author=Benson Yee |title=Transformers Movie (2007) Review |work=Ben's World of Transformers |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2013-08-07 |url=http://www.bwtf.com/movies/2007/ |accessdate=2009-02-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130807130735/http://bwtf.com/movies/2007/ }}</ref>。

电影为变形金刚系列产品大幅提升了知名度，吸引了众多新粉丝<ref>{{cite news |title='Transformers' fans never stopped playing |work=msnbc.com |date=2007-06-15 |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/id/19251314 |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102175022/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/19251314/ |archivedate=2012-11-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。其商业上的成功也催生了将《[[聖戰士_(VOLTRON)|聖戰士]]》和《[[太空堡垒|太空堡垒]]》改编写电影的计划<ref>{{cite news |author=Borys Kit |title=Maguire, WB attack the big screen with 'Robotech' |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2007-09-07 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/maguire-wb-attack-big-screen-149582 |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021081025/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/maguire-wb-attack-big-screen-149582 |archivedate=2012-10-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，还包括《霹雳游侠》的重拍<ref>{{cite news |author=Josef Adalian |title=NBC taps Liman for 'Knight Rider' |work=Variety |date=2007-09-26 |archivedate=2013-07-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130718191210/http://variety.com/2007/scene/news/nbc-taps-liman-for-knight-rider-1117972829/ |url=http://variety.com/2007/scene/news/nbc-taps-liman-for-knight-rider-1117972829/ |accessdate=2013-09-10 }}</ref>。拍摄续集期间，一些军人告诉导演迈克尔·贝，《变形金刚》有助于让他们的孩子理解自己父亲的事业，许多人都给他们的[[水牛地雷防護車|水牛地雷防護車]]起了与变形金刚角色相同的名字，电影中的这种车正是碎骨魔的原型<ref>{{cite news |author=Brian Savage |title=TCC Exclusive: Transformers Revenge of the Fallen at Toy Fair 2009 |work=Transformers Collectors Club |url=http://www.transformersclub.com/tfrof-intv09.cfm |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archivedate=2013-05-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528051946/http://www.transformersclub.com/tfrof-intv09.cfm |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

电影2009年发行的续集片名定为《變形金剛：復仇之戰》后，罗伯特·奥奇曾被问起本片是否会重新命名，就像1977年的《[[星球大战|星球大战]]》重新发行时命名为《[[星際大戰四部曲：曙光乍現|星際大戰四部曲：曙光乍現]]》一样。奥奇估计这一可能性不大，但如果真要更名，他会用《变形金刚：别有洞天》（{{lang|en|Transformers: More Than Meets the Eye}}，意译）<ref>{{cite web |author=Roberto Orci |title=The All New "Hey Roberto" Thread |publisher=Don Murphy |date=2008-07-11 |url=http://www.donmurphy.net/board/showpost.php?p=1199981&postcount=14057 |accessdate=2008-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120227103623/http://www.donmurphy.net/board/showpost.php?p=1199981&postcount=14057 |archive-date=2012-02-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
《变形金刚》在影评人中获得的评价褒贬不一。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的221篇专业评论文章，其中127篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为57%，平均得分5.8（最高10分）<ref>{{cite web |archivedate=2013-05-08 |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/transformers_the_movie |deadurl=no |work=Rotten Tomatoes |title=Transformers |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508055114/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/transformers_the_movie/ |accessdate=2017-06-10 }}</ref>。而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上收集的35篇评论中有26篇给出好评，2篇差评，7篇褒贬不一，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]61（满分100）<ref name="meta">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/transformers |publisher=Metacritic |title=Transformers |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archivedate=2012-10-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024055810/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/transformers }}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]网站的托德·吉尔克里斯特（{{lang|en|Todd Gilchrist}}）称这是[[迈克尔·贝|迈克尔·贝]]最优秀的电影，是“为数不多的几部可以让人同时对其中的聪明和愚蠢感到满意的作品之一，这主要是因为片中无可否认地拥有很多有趣的东西”<ref name="gilchrist">{{cite news |author=Todd Gilchrist |title=Advance Review: Transformers |work=IGN |date=2007-06-29 |archivedate=2013-06-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601040315/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/06/30/advance-review-transformers |deadurl=no |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/06/30/advance-review-transformers |accessdate=2013-09-09 }}</ref>。《[[广告商_(报纸)|广告商]]》（{{lang|en|The Advertiser}}）的肖恩·福斯特（{{lang|en|Sean Fewster}}）认为片中的视觉特技堪称天衣无缝，“你可能会以为电影公司真的实现了人工智能”<ref>{{cite news |author=Sean Fewster |title=The rule of robots begins |work=The Advertiser |date=2007-06-25 |url=http://www.news.com.au/adelaidenow/story/0,22606,21963548-5006343,00.html |accessdate=2008-04-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080403032930/http://www.news.com.au/adelaidenow/story/0%2C22606%2C21963548-5006343%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-04-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[丹佛邮报|丹佛邮报]]》（{{lang|en|The Denver Post}}）的丽莎·肯尼迪（{{lang|en|Lisa Kennedy}}）称赞片中对机器人的描述拥有“可信的尺度呈现和亲切感”<ref>{{cite news|author=Lisa Kennedy|title="Transformers" toys with human emotions|work=The Denver Post|date=2007-07-01|url=http://www.denverpost.com/entertainment/ci_6270283|accessdate=2007-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070705070856/http://www.denverpost.com/entertainment/ci_6270283|archive-date=2007-07-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[ABC电视|ABC]]节目主持人[[玛格丽特·彭慕兰|玛格丽特·彭慕兰]]（{{lang|en|Margaret Pomeranz}}）对片中“一个像我这样对变形金刚完全一无所知的人牵扯进这些巨型机器命运”的设定感到惊喜<ref>{{cite news|author=Margaret Pomeranz|title=Transformers|work=ABC Television|url=http://www.abc.net.au/atthemovies/txt/s1950144.htm|accessdate=2007-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011042025/http://abc.net.au/atthemovies/txt/s1950144.htm|archive-date=2007-10-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[Ain't_It_Cool_News|Ain't It Cool News]]}}网站的德鲁·麦克威尼（{{lang|en|Drew McWeeny}}）觉得大多数角色都融入到了故事里，而这一点在大量特技泛滥的今天是一个真正的奇迹<ref>{{cite news |author=Drew McWeeny |title=Moriarty Makes First Contact With TRANSFORMERS! The Movie, The Comics, The Books & More! |publisher=Ain't It Cool News |date=2007-07-02 |url=http://www.aintitcool.com/?q=node/33213 |accessdate=2008-06-26 |archivedate=2008-06-26 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080626165828/http://www.aintitcool.com/?q=node%2F33213 }}</ref>。作家[[彼得·大卫|彼得·大卫]]（{{lang|en|Peter David}}）称赞导演成功地一直吊起观众的胃口，最终呈现出了一些真正壮观的战斗场面<ref>{{cite news |author=Peter David |title=Car Toon |publisher=Self-published |archivedate=2012-07-28 |deadurl=no |date=2007-07-07 |url=http://peterdavid.malibulist.com/archives/005515.html#more |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728105936/http://www.peterdavid.net/archives/005515.html#more }}</ref>。[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]也给予影片三星（最高四星）的正面评价<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/transformers-2007 |work=Chicago Sun-Times |title=Transformers |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archivedate=2013-06-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602101141/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/transformers-2007 }}</ref>。

虽然电影的视觉效果获得了赞誉，但影评人对人类的故事情节有不同看法。《[[荷里活報道|荷里活報道]]》的柯克·哈尼科特（{{lang|en|Kirk Honeycutt}}）喜欢片中“把一个少年的情节主线和世界末日捆绑在一起”的做法<ref>{{cite news |author=Kirk Honeycutt |title=Transformers: Sci-fi action that is both smart and funny |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2007-06-29 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/film/reviews/article_display.jsp?&rid=9431 |accessdate=2009-09-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090908020917/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/film/reviews/article_display.jsp?&rid=9431 |archivedate=2009-09-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，而《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》的伊恩·内森（{{lang|en|Ian Nathan}}）则称赞希亚·拉博夫是“一个聪明、有天份的喜剧演员”，称他把握了这个玩具故事中直率和讽刺的平衡<ref>{{cite news |author=Ian Nathan |title=Transformers |work=Empire |url=http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=11052 |accessdate=2013-09-09 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2012-10-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014201137/http://www.empireonline.com/reviews/reviewcomplete.asp?FID=11052 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|Ain't It Cool News}}网站的创始人[[哈里·诺尔斯|哈里·诺尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Harry Knowles}}）觉得迈克尔·贝的风格和斯皮尔伯格有冲突，称片中的军方故事线索只是在转移观众对萨姆的注意力<ref>{{cite news |author=Harry Knowles |title=Harry reviews TRANSFORMERS which isn't really more than meets the eye! |work=Ain't It Cool News |date=2007-07-03 |url=http://www.aintitcool.com/?q=node/33226 |accessdate=2007-07-03 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2008-06-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080626165830/http://www.aintitcool.com/?q=node%2F33226 }}</ref>。詹姆斯·伯拉迪尼（{{lang|en|James Berardinelli}}）很讨厌这部电影，他无法在动作戏中把角色联系起来，因此觉得影片冗长乏味<ref>{{cite news |author=James Berardinelli |title=Transformers |work=Reelviews |url=http://www.reelviews.net/movies/t/transformers.html |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613130001/http://www.reelviews.net/movies/t/transformers.html |archive-date=2015-06-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的肯尼斯·图兰（{{lang|en|Kenneth Turan}}）觉得片中的人类“毫无生气到有些奇怪，一直在那裹足不前消磨时间，等待那些大玩具来让镜头充实起来”<ref>{{cite news |author=Kenneth Turan |title='Transformers' heavy on plot |work=Los Angeles Times |date=2007-07-02 |url=http://www.calendarlive.com/movies/reviews/la-et-transformers2jul02,0,445321.story |accessdate=2007-07-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208122715/http://www.calendarlive.com/movies/reviews/la-et-transformers2jul02%2C0%2C445321.story |archivedate=2008-12-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，而{{lang|en|ComingSoon.net}}网站的约书亚·斯坦姆斯（{{lang|en|Joshua Stames}}）觉得那些变形金刚本来是“完全真实可信的，可一旦他们开口说话的那一瞬起，他们就还原成了几个糟糕的动画角色”<ref>{{cite news |author=Joshua Stames |title=Transformers |work=Comingsoon.net |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/reviewsnews.php?id=21711 |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archivedate=2012-10-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003062816/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/reviewsnews.php?id=21711 }}</ref>。《[[每日先驱报|每日先驱报]]》（{{lang|en|Daily Herald}}）的马特·阿拉多（{{lang|en|Matt Arado}}）对剧中变形金刚只比配角略多一点的戏份感到恼火，而且觉得电影中场有些低迷<ref>{{cite news|author=Matt Arado |title='Transformers' lacks substance |publisher=Daily Herald |date=2007-07-02}}</ref>。[[CNN|CNN]]的汤姆·查瑞提（{{lang|en|Tom Charity}}）对电影基于玩具的构思提出疑问，觉得电影“旨在吸引青年观众……但把我们这些人晾在一边纳闷[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]是不是又把目标降低了”<ref>{{cite news |author=Tom Charity |title=Review: Dim 'Transformers' thuds with action |publisher=CNN |date=2007-07-04 |archivedate=2011-01-31 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110131063440/http://edition.cnn.com/2007/SHOWBIZ/Movies/07/02/review.transformers/index.html |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2007/SHOWBIZ/Movies/07/02/review.transformers/index.html |accessdate=2013-09-09 }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
《变形金刚》是2007年全世界商业上最成功的非续集电影，如果包括续集，其7.09亿美元的票房成绩也可以在2007年的世界电影中排到第5位<ref name="boxmojo" />，仅次于《[[加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头|加勒比海盗3：世界的尽头]]》、《[[哈利波特：鳳凰會的密令_(電影)|哈利波特：鳳凰會的密令]]》、《[[蜘蛛侠3|蜘蛛侠3]]》和《[[史瑞克三世|史瑞克三世]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2007&p=.htm |title=2007 WORLDWIDE GROSSES |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-09 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-05-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130508233318/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?view2=worldwide&yr=2007&p=.htm }}</ref>，并且截止2013年9月10日也还可以在世界电影历史票房总榜上排到第58位<ref name="alltime" />。影片于2007年6月28日在包括[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]、[[新西兰|新西兰]]、[[新加坡|新加坡]]和[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]在内的10个国家上映，首周进账2950万美元，登上这全部10个国家的票房[[冠军|冠军]]宝座<ref>{{cite news |author=Dave McNary |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/news/shrek-tops-overseas-box-office-2-1117967937/ |work=Variety |title='Shrek' tops overseas box office, 'Transformers' int'l release brings in $34.7 mil |date=2007-07-01 |accessdate=2013-09-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081022092421/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117967937.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 |archivedate=2008-10-22 }}</ref>。电影在[[马来西亚|马来西亚]]收入520万美元，-{刷新}-了该国历史上的电影票房纪录<ref>{{cite news |author=Vicci Ho |title='Transformers' dominates Malaysia |work=Variety |date=2007-08-08 |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/news/transformers-dominates-malaysia-1117969893/ |accessdate=2013-09-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081022092441/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117969893.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 |archivedate=2008-10-22 }}</ref>。《变形金刚》于7月11日在[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]上映，收入3730万美元，成为该国继1997年的《[[泰坦尼克号_(1997年电影)|泰坦尼克号]]》后票房最高的外语电影<ref>{{cite news |author=Min Lee |title='Transformers' Strong Showing in China |work=The West Australian |date=2007-10-02 |url=http://www.thewest.com.au/default.aspx?MenuID=23&ContentID=42206 |accessdate=2008-04-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080423164200/http://www.thewest.com.au/default.aspx?MenuID=23&ContentID=42206 |archivedate=2008-04-23 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。其上映第一天就收入了300万美元，也-{刷新}-了该国外语片上映的纪录<ref>{{cite news |author=Dave McNary |title='Transformers' smashes China record |work=Variety |date=2007-07-13 |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/news/transformers-smashes-china-record-1117968497/ |accessdate=2013-09-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081022092436/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117968497.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 |archivedate=2008-10-22 }}</ref>。影片于7月27日在[[英国|英国]]正式上映，进账870万[[英镑|英镑]]，并在这个周末创下了电影上座率的新纪录。在英国电影票房排行榜上位居第二位，仅次于《[[辛普森一家大电影|辛普森一家大电影]]》<ref>{{cite news |title=Simpsons film tops record weekend |work=BBC News Online |date=2007-07-31 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6923830.stm |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008075723/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6923830.stm |archivedate=2011-10-08 }}</ref>。《变形金刚》还成为2007年度[[大韩民国|大韩民国]]观影人数最多的外语电影，并-{刷新}-影片的外汇收入纪录<ref>{{cite news |author=Daum communication |title='Transformer, the biggest number of audiences' |work=E-today |date=2007-12-28 |url=http://www.etoday.co.kr/news/section/newsview.php?TM=news&SM=0101&idxno=150911 |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150602084447/http://www.etoday.co.kr/news/section/newsview.php?TM=news&SM=0101&idxno=150911 |archive-date=2015-06-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在北美，《变形金刚》是2007年平均每家电影院或平均每张银幕收入最高的电影<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.slate.com/id/2194532/pagenum/all/ |title=Why We Need Movie Reviewers |accessdate=2011-08-24 |work=Slate |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2011-08-24 |date=2008-07-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110824063423/http://www.slate.com/id/2194532/pagenum/all/ }}</ref>。影片于7月2日20点开始进行预演，7月3日正式上映，其中单在美国的预演就收入了880万美元<ref>{{cite news |author=Pamela McClintock |title='Transformers' nabs hefty haul |work=Variety |date=2007-07-03 |archivedate=2008-10-22 |deadurl=no |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/news/transformers-nabs-hefty-haul-2-1117967996/ |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081022092426/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117967996.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 }}</ref>，正式上映当天则收入2780万美元，-{刷新}-了[[星期四|星期四]]上映电影票房的纪录，不过这个纪录之后被2012年的《[[蜘蛛人：驚奇再起|蜘蛛人：驚奇再起]]》打破<ref>{{cite news |last=Finke |first=Nikki |title='Amazing Spider-Man' Shatters Tuesday Opening Box Office Record With $35M |url=http://www.deadline.com/2012/07/spider-man-debuts-amazing-7-5m-midnights/ |accessdate=2013-09-09 |newspaper=Deadline Hollywood |date=2012-07-04 |archivedate=2012-10-23 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023095006/http://www.deadline.com/2012/07/spider-man-debuts-amazing-7-5m-midnights/ }}</ref>。不过，本片打破了《[[蜘蛛人2|蜘蛛人2]]》创下的7月4日票房纪录，收入达2900万美元<ref>{{cite news |author=DreamWorks, Paramount Pictures |title=Transformers' Week One Records |work=Comingsoon.net |url=http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/94307-transformers-week-one-records |date=2007-07-11 |accessdate=2009-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130413001254/http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/94307-transformers-week-one-records |archivedate=2013-04-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《变形金刚》在北美的4050家电影院上映<ref name="boxmojo" />，第一个周末就进账7050万美元，而上映首周则达到1.55亿美元，创下了非续集电影的首周票房新纪录<ref>{{cite news |author=Pamela McClintock |title='Transformers' change weekend take |work=Variety |archivedate=2008-10-22 |deadurl=no |date=2007-07-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081022092432/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117968252.html?categoryid=13&cs=1 |url=http://variety.com/2007/film/news/transformers-change-weekend-take-1117968252/ |accessdate=2013-09-09 }}</ref>。这个成绩比派拉蒙电影公司的预期还要高50%，该公司的一位高层将之归功于[[口口相传|口口相传]]效应，让家长们知道“可以带上孩子（去看）”。一位市场调查显示电影最受儿童及其包括年长女性在内的家长们欢迎，还吸引了许多[[非裔美国人|非裔]]和[[拉丁裔美国人|拉丁裔]]观众走进电影院<ref>{{cite news |author=Nikki Finke |title='Transformers' Huge $152M First Week Sets 7-Day Non-Sequel Record Past 'Spidey', 'Passion' & 'Potter' |publisher=Deadline Hollywood Daily |date=2007-07-08 |url=http://www.deadlinehollywooddaily.com/transformers-on-target-for-150m-first-week/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318015513/http://www.deadlinehollywooddaily.com/transformers-on-target-for-150m-first-week/ |archivedate=2009-03-18 |accessdate=2010-06-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《变形金刚》在美国和加拿大的影院上映共计收入了3.19亿美元，是两国2007年的电影票房[[季军|季军]]，仅次于《蜘蛛侠3》和《史瑞克三世》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2007&p=.htm |title=2007 DOMESTIC GROSSES |publisher=Box Office Mojo |accessdate=2013-09-09 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2013-04-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130424234231/http://boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2007&p=.htm }}</ref>。

=== 荣誉 ===
《变形金刚》上映前，就在2007年[[MTV电影大奖|MTV电影大奖]]中经投票入选“你还没看过的最佳暑期电影”<ref>{{cite news |author=MTV |title=The MTV Movie Awards Winners! |work=ComingSoon.net |date=2007-06-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130823191246/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=20777 |archivedate=2013-08-23 |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=20777 |accessdate=2013-09-09 }}</ref>，之后又在[[2008年MTV電影大獎|2008年MTV電影大獎]]中当选为最佳影片。影片在[[第80届奥斯卡金像奖|第80届奥斯卡金像奖]]角逐中获得了音效剪辑、音效、视觉效果3项提名，但均未获奖，分别败给了《[[神鬼認證：最後通牒|神鬼認證：最後通牒]]》和《[[魔幻羅盤|魔幻羅盤]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/2000-present/2008/winners.html |title=80th Academy Awards nominations |publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |accessdate=2013-09-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120904101823/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/oscarlegacy/2000-present/2008/winners.html |archivedate=2012-09-04 }}</ref>。电影获2008年[[尼克频道儿童选择奖|儿童选择奖]]最受欢迎电影奖提名，但最终不敌《[[鼠來寶|鼠來寶]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.awn.com/news/awards/voting-underway-kids-choice-awards |title=Voting Underway for Kids' Choice Awards |publisher=Animation World Network |accessdate=2013-09-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902000418/http://www.awn.com/news/awards/voting-underway-kids-choice-awards |archivedate=2012-09-02 }}</ref>。影片在2007年[[吉隆坡国际电影节|吉隆坡国际电影节]]（{{lang|en|Kuala Lumpur International Film Festival}}）上获得了最佳特技效果评审团优异奖<ref>{{cite news |author=Carly Mayberry |title=KL fest wrapped on "Sunday" |work=Variety |date=2007-12-03 |url=http://www.varietyasiaonline.com/content/view/5077/53/ |accessdate=2007-09-08 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-02-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120209090039/http://www.varietyasiaonline.com/content/view/5077/53/ }}</ref>。视觉效果总监斯科特·法拉（{{lang|en|Scott Farrar}}）分别在好莱坞电影节和2007年10月22日举行的好莱坞颁奖晚会典礼上因在本片中的出色表现而获得了肯定<ref>{{cite news |author=Carly Mayberry |title=Hollywood fest to fete quartet |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2007-09-07 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/awards_festivals/news/e3idae648b19a12ff13b359ab0ff4228a50 |accessdate=2007-10-11 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20071011085558/http://hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/awards_festivals/news/e3idae648b19a12ff13b359ab0ff4228a50 |archivedate=2007-10-11 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2008年，视觉效果协会授予《变形金刚》4个奖项，分别是“以视效带动”类电影最佳视觉效果和最佳单场视觉效果桥段（片中擎天柱和碎骨魔的大战），另外两个奖项分别针对电影的[[比例模型|微缩模型]]和合成两方面表现<ref>{{cite news |author=Carolyn Giardina |title='Transformers' tops VES nods |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2008-02-11 |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/transformers-tops-ves-nods-104510 |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024051529/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/transformers-tops-ves-nods-104510 |archivedate=2012-10-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[作曲家|作曲家]]史蒂夫·贾布隆斯基也获得了[[广播音乐公司|广播音乐公司]]（{{lang|en|Broadcast Music Incorporated}}）的肯定<ref>{{cite news |title=2008 BMI Film/TV Awards |work=Broadcast Music Incorporated |date=2008-05-21 |url=http://www.bmi.com/news/entry/536622 |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archivedate=2011-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606195141/http://www.bmi.com/news/entry/536622 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》将大黄蜂列为最受欢迎计算机合成角色的第4名<ref>{{cite news |title=Our 10 Favorite CG Characters |work=Entertainment Weekly |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20046918,00.html |accessdate=2013-09-09 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121006163051/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20046918%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-10-06 }}</ref>，而《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》则把擎天柱评为最优秀电影机器人的第30位<ref>{{cite news |author=Michael Moran |title=The 50 best movie robots |work=The Times |date=2007-07-25 |archivedate=2011-09-06 |deadurl=no |url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article2133609.ece |accessdate=2011-09-06 |location=London |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906044703/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article2133609.ece }}</ref>。而在另一方面，強·沃特因本片和《[[國家寶藏：古籍秘辛|國家寶藏：古籍秘辛]]》、《[[九月黎明|九月黎明]]》（{{lang|en|September Dawn}}）等4部电影而获第28届[[金酸莓奖|金酸莓奖]]最差男配角奖提名<ref>{{cite web |title=Razzies© 2007 Nominees |publisher=Razzies |url=http://www.razzies.com/history/28thNoms.asp |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archivedate=2013-01-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130121200312/http://www.razzies.com/history/28thNoms.asp |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0418279/awards |title=Awards for Transformers (2007) |publisher=Amazon |work=IMDb |accessdate=2013-09-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111214010327/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0418279/awards |archivedate=2011-12-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 家用媒体 ===
《变形金刚》于2007年10月16日发行了第一区的[[DVD|DVD]]，同时发行的还有[[HD_DVD|HD DVD]]格式。其中[[沃尔玛|沃尔玛]]版本的DVD中包含前作漫画的缩减动画版本，名为《变形金刚起源》（{{lang|en|Transformers Beginnings}}），其中有马克·瑞恩、彼得·庫倫、凯文·杜恩和弗兰克·维尔克配音<ref name=walmart>{{cite news |title=Exclusive Transformers Movie Comic & Animated Prequel Coming To Target & Wal-Mart |work=Comic Books News International |date=2007-09-13 |url=http://comicnewsi.com/article.php?catid=208&itemid=10370 |accessdate=2007-10-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101121101758/http://comicnewsi.com/article.php?itemid=10370&catid=208 |archivedate=2010-11-21 }}</ref>。而[[塔吉特百貨公司|塔吉特]]版本则是一个擎天柱变形的DVD盒，还有一本有关霸天虎的漫画书<ref name=walmart />。DVD发行后，首周售出了830万份，是2007年销售速度最快的DVD，HD DVD在北美共售出19万份，创下了该格式单片销售的新纪录<ref>{{cite news |author=Mike Snider |title=Bay says 'Transformers' DVD could have been better |work=USA Today |date=2007-10-22 |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/dvd/2007-10-22-transformers-bay_N.htm |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025212200/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/dvd/2007-10-22-transformers-bay_N.htm |archivedate=2012-10-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。DVD一共售出了1374万份，也是2007年最畅销的<ref>{{cite news |author=Mike Snider |title=DVD feels first sting of slipping sales |work=USA Today |date=2008-01-07 |url=http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-01-07-dvd-sales-slippage_N.htm |accessdate=2009-09-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025212206/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2008-01-07-dvd-sales-slippage_N.htm |archivedate=2012-10-25 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

电影于2008年9月2日发行了[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Transformers 2007 Movie Out On Blu Ray Today |work=Seibertron |date=2008-09-02 |archivedate=2012-10-21 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021145619/http://www.seibertron.com/transformers/news/transformers-2007-movie-out-on-blu-ray-today/13875/ |url=http://www.seibertron.com/transformers/news/transformers-2007-movie-out-on-blu-ray-today/13875/ |accessdate=2013-09-09 }}</ref>。其中的双碟版本首周就成为最畅销的电影蓝光影碟，占该周影片DVD销售量的三分之二，在所有DVD销量版上仍然可以排到第3位<ref>{{cite news |title=Movie DVD Sales #1 On Blu-ray, #3 Overall Last Week |work=TFormers |date=2008-09-11 |url=http://tformers.com/transformers-movie-dvd-sales-1-on-blu-ray-3-overall-last-week/10138/news.html |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archivedate=2012-02-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218034128/http://tformers.com/transformers-movie-dvd-sales-1-on-blu-ray-3-overall-last-week/10138/news.html }}</ref>。2009年6月16日，派拉蒙在所有新的《变形金刚》DVD中包括了一张贴纸，其中包含有可以用来在线观看首部电影独家内容的代码，还可以抢先欣赏续集《變形金剛：復仇之戰》，内容包括三段《變形金剛：復仇之戰》的独家片段，两部电影的幕后片段和第一部电影的一些从未发行过的删除镜头<ref>{{cite web |title=Transformers Bonus Material Coming June 16 |work=Superhero Hype! |archivedate=2012-10-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020212759/http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/98921-transformers-bonus-material-coming-june-16 |url=http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/98921-transformers-bonus-material-coming-june-16 |accessdate=2013-09-09 }}</ref>。截止2013年9月9日，DVD在北美地区已经售出了超过1625万份，收入超过2.92亿美元<ref>{{cite web |title=Transformers DVD sales |work=The Numbers |url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2007/TFORM-DVD.php |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131006205749/http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/2007/TFORM-DVD.php |archive-date=2013-10-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 续集 ==
{{main|變形金剛：復仇之戰|變形金剛3|变形金刚4|變形金剛5}}
2009年6月24日，电影的[[续集|续集]]《[[變形金剛：復仇之戰|變形金剛：復仇之戰]]》上映，虽然所获专业评价惨不忍睹，但商业上仍然非常成功，票房更胜前作<ref name="alltime" />。2011年6月29日，第二部续集《[[變形金剛3|變形金剛3]]》以[[三維電影|3-D]]模式上映，评价仍然较差，但票房突破11亿美元<ref name="alltime" />。2014年6月27日，第4部《变形金刚》电影《[[变形金刚4|变形金刚4]]》发行，票房超过10亿美元，成为[[2014年电影|2014年世界电影票房冠军]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=transformers4.htm | title = Transformers: Age of Extinction | publisher = IMDb.com | work = Box Office Mojo | accessdate = 2015-01-03 | archivedate = 2014-09-16 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140916031156/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=transformers4.htm }}</ref>。第5部《变形金刚》系列电影于2017年上映<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cineeurope-paramount-screens-transformers-age-712745 | title = CineEurope: Paramount Screens 'Transformers: Age of Extinction' One Day Before World Premiere | last = Kemp | first = Stuart | work = The Hollywood Reporter | date = 2014-06-18 | accessdate = 2014-07-22 | archivedate = 2014-07-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140722024452/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cineeurope-paramount-screens-transformers-age-712745 }}</ref>，迈克尔·贝繼續出任导演<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | url = http://variety.com/2014/film/news/michael-bay-eyes-action-pic-13-hours-in-benghazi-for-paramount-1201331192/ | title = Michael Bay Eyes Benghazi Pic '13 Hours' for Paramount | publisher = Variety | last = Kroll | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150103005753/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/michael-bay-eyes-action-pic-13-hours-in-benghazi-for-paramount-1201331192/ | first = Justin | date = 2014-10-30 | archivedate = 2015-01-03 | access-date = 2015-01-03 }}</ref>。

